ple" title="Omuma people">Omuma</a> &#160;<span style="font-weight:bold;">·</span>  <a href="/wiki/Onitsha-Ado" title="Onitsha-Ado">Onitsha</a> &#160;<span style="font-weight:bold;">·</span>  <a href="/wiki/Oratta" title="Oratta">Oratta</a> &#160;<span style="font-weight:bold;">·</span>  <a href="/wiki/Bonny" title="Bonny">Ubani</a> &#160;<span style="font-weight:bold;">·</span>  <a href="/wiki/Ukwuani_people" title="Ukwuani people">Ukwuani</a></div>
